#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.isin.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.isin"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:1 of
msgid ""
"Calculates `element in test_elements`, broadcasting over `element` only. "
"Returns a boolean array of the same shape as `element` that is True where"
" an element of `element` is in `test_elements` and False otherwise."
msgstr ""
"计算 `element in test_elements`，仅对 `element` 进行广播。返回一个与 `"
"element` 形状相同的布尔数组，当 `element` 中的元素在 `test_elements` 中时"
"为 True，否则为 False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:5 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:7 of
msgid ""
"The values against which to test each value of `element`. This argument "
"is flattened if it is a tensor or array_like. See notes for behavior with"
" non-array-like parameters."
msgstr ""
"用于测试 `element` 中每个值的值。如果该参数是张量或 array_like，则会被"
"展平。有关非类数组参数的行为，请参见说明。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:11 of
msgid ""
"If True, the input tensors are both assumed to be unique, which can speed"
" up the calculation.  Default is False."
msgstr "如果为 True，则假定输入张量都是唯一的，这可以加快计算速度。默认为 False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:14 of
msgid ""
"If True, the values in the returned tensor are inverted, as if "
"calculating `element not in test_elements`. Default is False. "
"``mt.isin(a, b, invert=True)`` is equivalent to (but faster than) "
"``mt.invert(mt.isin(a, b))``."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则返回张量中的值会被反转，如同计算 `element not in test_"
"elements`。默认为 False。``mt.isin(a, b, invert=True)`` 等价于（但比）``"
"mt.invert(mt.isin(a, b))`` 更快。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:20 of
msgid ""
"**isin** -- Has the same shape as `element`. The values `element[isin]` "
"are in `test_elements`."
msgstr ""
"**isin** -- 与 `element` 具有相同的形状。`element[isin]` 的值在 `test_"
"elements` 中。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`in1d`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:27 of
msgid "Flattened version of this function."
msgstr "此函数的展平版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:30 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:31 of
msgid ""
"`isin` is an element-wise function version of the python keyword `in`. "
"``isin(a, b)`` is roughly equivalent to ``mt.array([item in b for item in"
" a])`` if `a` and `b` are 1-D sequences."
msgstr ""
"`isin` 是 Python 关键字 `in` 的逐元素函数版本。如果 `a` 和 `b` 是一维序列"
"，则 ``isin(a, b)`` 大致等价于 ``mt.array([item in b for item in a])``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:35 of
msgid ""
"`element` and `test_elements` are converted to tensors if they are not "
"already. If `test_elements` is a set (or other non-sequence collection) "
"it will be converted to an object tensor with one element, rather than a "
"tensor of the values contained in `test_elements`. This is a consequence "
"of the `tensor` constructor's way of handling non-sequence collections. "
"Converting the set to a list usually gives the desired behavior."
msgstr ""
"`element` 和 `test_elements` 如果不是张量则会被转换为张量。如果 `test_"
"elements` 是一个集合（或其他非序列集合），它将被转换为一个包含一个元素的"
"对象张量，而不是包含 `test_elements` 中的值的张量。这是 `tensor` 构造函数"
"处理非序列集合的方式造成的。将集合转换为列表通常能得到期望的行为。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:43 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:64 of
msgid ""
"Because of how `array` handles sets, the following does not work as "
"expected:"
msgstr "由于 `array` 处理集合的方式，以下操作不会按预期工作："

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.isin.isin:72 of
msgid "Casting the set to a list gives the expected result:"
msgstr "将集合转换为列表可以得到预期结果："

